author: BBC
title: Pro-Europe referendum group launches
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device Pro-Europe referendum group launches 11 October 2015 Last updated at 22:55 BST
Monday sees the formal launch of the campaign to keep Britain in the European Union.
Businessman Lord Rose, the former head of Marks & Spencer, will lead the Britain Stronger in Europe group ahead of the forthcoming European referendum.
The groups spearheading the push to leave have already got their campaigns under way, as Eleanor Garnier reports.
Read more UKIP's Nigel Farage: I support both EU 'Out' campaigns
